name: Travelling for power
description:
All of us just seek more power. All of us just travel to higher amounts of true strength. All of us seek that depths.

But not all of us are knowing how and why, we do it instinctively, and if we look at our past mistakes, acting instinctively brought us more pain than joy and fulfillment.  Gotta find the true ways and know our personal one. 

Let's get acquired by the true travelling to great knowns/unknowns.

This piece will have a "mandala" piece sold also separately :)
